    excerpt: "The undisputed heavyweight champion of the world is being confronted at a McDonald\u2019s on Khreshchatyk in Kyiv. A stranger decides to start something with Oleksandr Usyk. Usyk does not square up. He refuses to engage, and the way he does it is almost playful.",
